title: Smalltown Poets Discography 1995-2013 (9 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
SMALLTOWN POETS DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 9 releases...

 * 1995 - Villanelle - Pinwheels And Orange Peels
 * 1997 - Smalltown Poets
 * 1998 - Listen Closely
 * 2000 - Third Verse
 * 2004 - It's Later Than Its Ever Been
 * 2011 - Smalltown Poets Christmas
 * 2012 - Grace Is A Song - Single
 * 2012 - Under The New Sun
 * 2013 - Turn Around - Single

Smalltown Poets is a Christian rock band formed in 1996.  The band started under the name Villanelle.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - November 2013
